      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Patch tests and benchmark problems (NAFEMS LE1, LE10) executed for all element types used. Results within 1% of analytical solutions. Achieved level 3 satisfies required level 2."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
