    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for model risk level 3. The single below-threshold factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is acknowledged; the assessment team determined that the remaining factor performance, multi-laboratory experimental basis, and quantitative output comparison collectively provide sufficient credibility to support the intended regulatory submission. Overall credibility is accepted with the recommendation that additional test conditions be incorporated in future model updates.",
